						<div class="postbody">So this could work with a Game Genie and any cartridge with battery backed SRAM?  So then you can develop and run games which run entirely from the SRAM area, and take advantage of the CHR RAM built into the cartridge.  Of course, you'd need to override the vectors.
<br />
<br />But I'm a total hardware klutz, don't have soldering irons laying around nor random resistors, and can't build the cable.</div>

					
